    <headline>Heavy rain, yellow level, Parts of Hordaland, 2022-09-12T14:00:00+00:00, 2022-09-13T04:00:00+00:00</headline>
    <description>From Monday afternoon til Tuesday morning heavy rain is expected, locally can come 50-65 mm/12t. The most intense precipitation is expected in Sunnhordland.</description>
    <instruction>The need for emergency preparedness shall be assessed continuously by emergency response actors. Check road reports (175.no). Adjust the speed and use caution while driving. </instruction>
